race.description: Victor Harbor Motor Co Maiden Plate
race.comment: PRETTY PERKY (9) took a solid step forward second-up when chasing gamely into the placings at headquarters. Peaking now and has the early dash to offset the wide alley. With the light weight, she'll be hard to reel in. YOU'RESOGOLDEN (10) gave a bold sight on debut here 10 days ago, only grabbed late. Draws to advantage and strips fitter, so she should again prove very hard to catch. FOUR PINETINIS (4) is a Denman gelding on debut for the sharp juvenile yard of  R & C Jolly. Has shown good signs in his lead-up work and picks up the key booking of Toeroek. A bright start looks likely. PRETTY MORSEL (6) has been knocking on the door and was strong here last time, closing off well to just miss. Cherry-ripe now and sure to be competitive. OLIVIA MARIE (8) is a Bivouac filly on debut for the Oxlade team. She's impressed in her lead-up work and can make the perfect start.
